title: DS310.04 Getting Started with DSE Search | DataStax Enterprise 6 Search
description:
#DataStaxAcademy #DS310
DS310.04 Getting Started with DSE Search
In this section, we will learn about enabling Search on DataStax Enterprise and creating search indexes on tables that can be used for search queries. 

LEARN FOR FREE at https://academy.datastax.com -- access all the FREE complete courses, tutorials, and hands-on exercises.

ASK QUESTIONS at https://community.datastax.com -- where experts from DataStax & the Apache Cassandra community share their expertise everyday.
